            The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Afterword</ENAMEX> concludes with a look at words as
single <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">entities</ENAMEX>.  It is divided into <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> sections--geometric
