On the tip of one's tongue
The written word
Words and the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">poet</ENAMEX>
Sticks and <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">stones</ENAMEX>: words as reality

            

            There is an <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Afterword</ENAMEX> that is even friendlier than
